---
title: Topik
layout: main
---

<main>
  <h2>Topik</h2>
  <p style="color: var(--meta-color); margin-top: -0.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">
    Kumpulan topik dari tulisan-tulisan di situs ini.
  </p>

  <div class="articles">
    {%- for tag in collections.tagList %}
      {%- set count = collections[tag] | length %}
      <div class="article">
        <a href="/tags/{{ tag | url }}/">
          <h6>&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp; {{ tag }} <span style="opacity: .65">({{ count }})</span></h6>
        </a>
      </div>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>

  <a class="back" href="/">&lt; Kembali ke halaman utama</a>
</main>
